    public interface EventListener
extends Any
    Definition of an event listener to which an com.inqwell.any.EventGenerator will send events. These interfaces together define a 'push' model of event propagation, whereby action in a target is inspired directly by com.inqwell.any.EventGenerator.fireEvent().

      • getDesiredEventTypes

        Array getDesiredEventTypes()
        Returns the event types this listener would like to listen to. Can be called by an EventGenerator's addEventListener() methods for those cases where the generator supports subscription to specific event types and the listener wishes to specify the event types it wants to receive notification of.
